  • Enum Constant Summary

    Enum Constants
    Enum Constant
    Description
    AUTO
    A type of auto indicates that the marker is oriented such that its positive x-axis is pointing in the direction of the path at the point it is place.
    AUTO_START_REVERSE
    A type of auto-start-reverse means the same as AUTO except that for a marker placed by "marker-start", the orientation is 180° different from the orientation as determined by auto.
